{"tid":2023452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：要求立法會暑假休會前完成引入中國法律法案","createTime":"2020-05-19T04:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T04:40:17.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5aa4d618a2a6ed8bdaf78aa567cb173b9829eae6","tid":2023452,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"張建宗冀立法會7月暑假休會前完成審議31個立法項目<br />\n19.05.2020 12:14<br />\n<br />\n政務司長張建宗去信立法會主席梁君彥，指今屆立法會會期只剩下9個星期和8次會議，政府期待立法會可以盡量完成審議31項法案和決議案，包括《國歌條例草案》、禁止電子煙草案、專營的士草案、延長產假草案、委任張舉能為終審法院首席法官的議案等。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗表示，如果這些立法項目在今屆會期完結時未獲通過，就將會失效，希望梁君彥制訂會議安排時，能考慮立法項目擠壓情況，也懇請立法會抓緊時間，盡快完成立法程序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288471&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288471%26csid%3D261_341&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=9b965e6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288471&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"f3ab268eecf6210d5fa0e409254dfc7919f9c315","tid":2023452,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fc7114f23a97c82dfc924e72dff5b346f4d08f","tid":2023452,"uid":228868,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"換美金呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ab7f411fbfccb219fbdd882819493a37c1b602","tid":2023452,"uid":128923,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"低能 禁止電子煙根本唔夠票過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img